{"root":{"data":{"id":"d1l1e58plr0g","created":1716874997098,"text":"WGS-AST模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1l1ezu4q8lc","created":1716875063697,"text":"数据集分配","priority":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1l3y3klk16o","created":1716882202966,"text":"数据：筛选的1942株菌株"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1ls3qdf2u4g","created":1716950351057,"text":"原则：根据MLST结果，将菌株按8:2的分层抽样比例随机分配"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1ls51fi7jls","created":1716950453492,"text":"最终数据：训练集(n = 1557)和测试集(n = 385)"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1l1f1k5o6bk","created":1716875067447,"text":"数据集处理","priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1ls7c31qebk","created":1716950633411,"text":"1.使用BLASTN将基因组序列与整理好的ARG参考数据库进行比对"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1ls8m6iak8w","created":1716950733753,"text":"软件版本:ncbi-blast-2.9.0+"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1ls8qupmww0","created":1716950743923,"text":"比对参数:- value 1e-5 -outfmt 0 -num_alignments 10000"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1ls96xumrk0","created":1716950778941,"text":"输出格式是m0格式"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1ls7pwzvsow","created":1716950663520,"text":"2.利用自建的Perl脚本程序解析m0格式比对结果，获得抗生素耐药基因的SNP/InDels"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lvo23xsa9s","created":1716960407218,"text":"3.仅保留identity ≥ 90% 和 subject coverage ≥ 60%的比对结果"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwdxcy5p1c","created":1716962434347,"text":"4.对于每个contig的比对区域，选择具有最大值(hit_score*subject_coverage)的结果作为最佳比对结果并进行注释"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwfz4yr0g0","created":1716962594946,"text":"5.对检测到的ARG拷贝数进行计数，计算公式：ARG拷贝数=(目标ARG覆盖率*覆盖区域深度)/(菌株基因组覆盖率*基因组覆盖区域深度)"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1l1f33kgrnk","created":1716875070798,"text":"模型训练","priority":3},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwhj6gk3k0","created":1716962716936,"text":"一对病原体和抗生素组合探索基因组特征与AST\n结果之间的关系使用这3个模型进行计算"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwioyynda8","created":1716962807908,"text":"广义线性模型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwiqmvqxvk","created":1716962811531,"text":"随机森林模型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwirno035s","created":1716962813755,"text":"LASSO回归模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwjwrftjwg","created":1716962903231,"text":"相比其他两个模型，LASSO回归模型有效地解决了共线性和过拟合问题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwk398w54w","created":1716962917369,"text":"浓度-时间曲线下面积(AUC)值大于0.9，表现出同样良好的性能"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwkm6hon40","created":1716962958561,"text":"该模型最终用于评估每个筛选的关键ARG对抗性表型的贡献，并计算ARG系数(权重)"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwluj83s3k","created":1716963055109,"text":"模型训练过程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwmodsscn4","created":1716963120085,"text":"将遗传数据转化为0 ~ 1型矩阵，其中1表示检测到ARG或ARG变异"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwmxpu3g8w","created":1716963140404,"text":"使用R glmnet软件包构建LASSO回归模型，并进行10倍交叉验证"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwoxf7991c","created":1716963296489,"text":"LASSO回归分类器使用不同大小的随机子样本进行训练"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwp4z43bwg","created":1716963312931,"text":"在训练数据集中重复10次"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwpentufi8","created":1716963334016,"text":"对于每种病原体/抗生素组合模型，在10次嵌套交叉验证中记录10次AUC值"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwn98zdg5c","created":1716963165506,"text":"计算AUC来评价每个模型的性能","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwpjdq98g0","created":1716963344289,"text":"利用AUC值分布来评价样本量是否足够"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwngwfisxs","created":1716963182161,"text":"筛选的关键ARG亚型所属ARG族的权重系数公式："},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1ls77un308w","created":1716950624196,"text":"模型训练结果","priority":4},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwwfm2yygw","created":1716963884636,"text":"鲍曼不动杆菌抗性特征"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwwpi76l1c","created":1716963906169,"text":"IPM：20个"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lwxr74ts00","created":1716963988218,"text":"IPM的耐药特征包括OXA-23、OXA-24、\nOXA-72、NDM-1、IMP-16、部分ADC亚型和部分低频率的OXA亚型","layout_right_offset":{"x":1,"y":0}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwwwbgxxxc","created":1716963921000,"text":"CAZ：31个"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwx7f21tds","created":1716963945161,"text":"CPM：24个"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lwxb5u969s","created":1716963953311,"text"